#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:68
msgid "Online Inference on NPU"
msgstr "NPU 在线推理"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:71
msgid ""
"For Atlas 300I DUO (310P), do not rely on `max-model-len` auto detection "
"(that is, do not omit the `--max-model-len` argument), because it may "
"cause OOM."
msgstr ""
"对于 Atlas 300I DUO (310P)，请不要依赖 `max-model-len` 的自动检测（即不要省略 `--max-model-len` 参数），因为这可能导致 OOM。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:74
msgid "Reason, based on the current 310P attention path:"
msgstr "原因（基于当前 310P 注意力路径）："

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:76
msgid ""
"`AscendAttentionMetadataBuilder310` passes `model_config.max_model_len` "
"to `AttentionMaskBuilder310`."
msgstr ""
"`AscendAttentionMetadataBuilder310` 将 `model_config.max_model_len` 传递给 `AttentionMaskBuilder310`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:78
msgid ""
"`AttentionMaskBuilder310` builds a full causal mask with shape "
"`[max_model_len, max_model_len]` in float16, then converts it to "
"FRACTAL_NZ."
msgstr ""
"`AttentionMaskBuilder310` 构建一个形状为 `[max_model_len, max_model_len]` 的完整因果掩码（使用 float16），然后将其转换为 FRACTAL_NZ 格式。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:80
msgid ""
"In the 310P `attention_v1` prefill/chunked-prefill path "
"(`_npu_flash_attention` / `_npu_paged_attention_splitfuse`), this "
"explicit mask tensor is consumed directly, and there is currently no "
"compressed-mask path."
msgstr ""
"在 310P 的 `attention_v1` 预填充/分块预填充路径（`_npu_flash_attention` / `_npu_paged_attention_splitfuse`）中，此显式掩码张量被直接使用，并且目前没有压缩掩码路径。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/hardwares/310p.md:85
msgid ""
"If auto detection resolves to a large context length, the mask allocation"
" (`O(max_model_len^2)`) may exceed NPU memory and trigger OOM. Always set"
" an explicit and conservative value, for example `--max-model-len 16384`."
msgstr ""
"如果自动解析出的上下文长度较大，掩码分配（`O(max_model_len^2)`）可能会超出 NPU 内存并触发 OOM。请始终设置一个保守的显式值，例如 `--max-model-len 16384`。"

